data.description: Welcome to this recently renovated home that include 3 bedroom plus Bonus Room and 1700 sq. ft. of living space!!  This Home comes a great location close to services and convenience stores as well as Walking Distance to all schools, spacious floor-plan, new laminate flooring, new bathroom fixtures, New light/ceiling fixtures, new bath fixtures, new interior paint, granite kitchen counters, and a quiet place in Apple Valley. Close to shopping and convenience stores schools and other amenities. Nearly Half Acre lot with RV access on both sides of home and 3 spacious storage sheds to keep all tools and gardening equipment. Home is Rock-scaped in the front yard and the backyard offers a covered patio (SPA ROOM) area for those summer or rainy days as well as plenty of space for projects such as an ADU, pool etc. Enjoy the fresh air and warm climate, mountain views the High Desert has to offer from this home.... Come See Today!!
